🏦 Loan Approval Demo: Tool Selection Strategy
🎯 Goal
Showcase a modular, agentic loan approval flow with schema validation, test generation, compliance checks, and orchestration—using free or open-source tools where possible.

🧰 Recommended Tool Stack (Demo-Ready & Cost-Efficient)
Layer	Tool	Purpose	Cost
Agent Orchestration	Crew AI	Multi-agent routing	✅ Free
LLM Agents	Ollama (local)	Schema synthesis, review	✅ Free
IDE Assist	GitHub Copilot	Code generation, YAML/SQL	⚠️ Paid (trial available)
Data Storage	DuckDB / SQLite	Local DB for schema + data	✅ Free
Validation	SQLFluff / dbt Core	Schema linting, testing	✅ Free
Test Generation	Great Expectations	Data quality checks	✅ Free
Monitoring	XAI Engine (basic logs)	Agent output traceability	✅ Free (custom Python)
Security	Role-based access (mocked)	Simulate IAM	✅ Free (demo logic)
Compliance	Ethical AI agent	RBI/FRB rule checks	✅ Free (rule-based logic)
UI Layer	Streamlit / Vibe Coding	Stakeholder dashboard	✅ Free
Data Ingestion	CSV / Parquet	Loan data input	✅ Free
Optional	Azure Blob / Azure SQL	Cloud storage	⚠️ Pay-as-you-go
🧠 Demo Flow Mapping to Architecture
Architecture Block	Demo Component
Business Workflow	Crew AI orchestrator
AI Agents	SchemaSynth, SQLGuard, TestGenie
Multi-Model Routing	Ollama + Copilot
DL/DWH	DuckDB or SQLite
Vector DB / Knowledge Graph	Optional (mocked for demo)
Risk Mitigation	Human-in-loop + Ethical AI agent
Monitoring	Logs + XAI-style agent trace
Security	Simulated IAM + prompt guardrails
CI/CD	GitHub triggers + auto-test
Unstructured Data	Loan documents (PDF/CSV)
CRM/Core Banking	Mocked tables for integration
📦 Suggested Demo Modules
Loan Intake: Upload CSV → SchemaSynth agent → SQL schema

Validation: SQLGuard agent → SQLFluff/dbt → schema linting

Test Generation: TestGenie agent → Great Expectations

Review: PRReviewer agent → feedback loop

Compliance Check: Ethical AI agent → RBI/FRB rules

Monitoring: Logs + agent trace

UI Dashboard: Streamlit or Vibe Coding
